title: Random Photo
description: Took these photos today pretty quickly so that I could be the first person to post on this site

title: My Life
description: An expression of how my life looks when compared to other peoples. It can look terrible and make you feel bad for me. It can look beautiful and make you jealous. It's how you look at it.

title: The World
description: This is the way the world is in the modern day. Real, raw, unedited photos of how our planet is doing.

title: Civilization
description: Humans have created civilizations for millions of years in many different places. These civilizations all look and behave differently from one another. That being said, why, when I say civilization do you picture something like this?

title: Nature
description: When untouched, nature is the most beautiful thing the world has to offer. It is the art of mother nature... Don't tarnish or dis-respect her art!

title: Home Improvement
description: Improvement is subjective to a degree, what is an improvement to many may be a downgrade to others.

title: Trash
description: This is Garbage... A.K.A Food.

title: Video Games
description: The ultimate form of escapism. This medium allows you to not only watch or hear the story of a person, you live that story as you take control of the person and run around in their world.

title: Open World
description: The term comes from video games, but I prefer to think of it as a philosophy for living my life. I live in an open world, so I want to explore it.
